<h3>1. Bookstore Application (JavaFX)</h3>
<p>
A desktop bookstore management system built with Java and JavaFX, featuring role-based access for owners and customers, file-backed data persistence, and a customer loyalty rewards program. The application supports secure login, dynamic inventory browsing, purchasing workflows, and points redemption logic. This project demonstrates skills in object-oriented design, GUI development, event-driven programming, and applying design patterns such as State to manage application behavior.
</p>

