<h3>4. Restaurant Ordering & Reservation DBMS</h3>
<p>
Designed and implemented a full-stack restaurant database system to manage customers, reservations, seating, menus, bills, and payments using Oracle SQL. The project involved defining functional dependencies, normalizing schemas to 3NF/BCNF, and writing complex SQL queries and scripts for data integrity. A simple Java/Python-based interface was used to interact with the database, showcasing skills in database design, normalization, SQL optimization, and backend integration.
</p>

