<h3>7. Weather Web App (React)</h3>
<p>
Created a responsive weather application using React and the OpenWeather API that displays real-time conditions, forecasts, and dynamic backgrounds based on weather states. The app uses React hooks, API integration, and component-based design to deliver an interactive user experience. This project demonstrates frontend development, asynchronous data fetching, and modern JavaScript practices.
</p>


